<h3>💎 <strong>NEW!</strong> Blogging feature.</h3>
<p>Place your posts in the <code>posts</code> folder with the following format:</p>
<pre><code class="language-text">[YYYY]-[MM]-[DD]-[TITLE].md
</code></pre>
<p>Your post archive can be found at <code>/posts</code>. <a href="https://hello-markdown.glitch.me/posts">Example of the posts archive.</a></p>

